Title: The Bees' Knees
Description:
You really hozen friend, wikket? Let's see, hmm?

Hozen at Grookin' Hill all outta slicky bait. Tigerflies' legs stay twitchy in water - make best bait!

Bo Bo sick from stings. Wikket get bait and take to Grookin.
ObjectivesText: Collect 30 Bug Legs from Tigerflies in Tigers' Wood.
